{"tid":2181166,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港康碼準備就緒　薛永恒稱需待疫情平穩始可推出","createTime":"2020-08-30T11:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T12:48:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6696b54b1c7a6ecbcb967d804f03980cc03f3240","tid":2181166,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:48:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546792-20200830.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546792-20200830.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoDw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=09501969\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546792-20200830.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=687eca07\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546792-20200830.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長薛永恒表示，香港健康碼已準備就緒，何時推出要視乎疫情何時平穩，例如有待確診宗數回落至單位數、沒有本地個案、疫情不再反覆等。<br />\n<br />\n對於有市民擔心，以港康碼取得粵港碼或澳康碼後，抵達廣東及澳門後可被追蹤。薛永恒認為，市民去到當地後，已成為社區中可互相感染的一分子，應配合當地防疫制度，屬情理之中，不認為港人可獲豁免。他又說，即使前往英、美等外地國家，亦要配合當地防疫要求。<br />\n<br />\n薛永恒提到，日後市民申請港康碼時，初時會有配額，取得配額後需前往衞生署指定的十多間化驗所接受核酸檢測，結果會上載至署方網站，亦會通知有關人士，若檢測呈陰性，就可取得港康碼以申請粵康碼及澳康碼，過關時可不用強制檢疫，形容措施便民、利民。"},{"pid":"d643268078b913dcb69be4bdedc3a33d251112a7","tid":2181166,"uid":152589,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:54:30.000Z","msg":"Dllm"},{"pid":"5c857f2265dfd8698ccff20c194fa62d111c8677","tid":2181166,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid